{
  "id": "helix-shadcn-init",
  "title": "Initialize shadcn/ui in apps/admin with components.json and Radix primitives",
  "category": "frontend",
  "description": "The admin app has 4 manually-created UI components (badge, card, table, tabs) but no `components.json` and no formal shadcn/ui setup. This creates inconsistency and makes adding new components manual.\n\n## What to do\n\n1. Run `npx shadcn@latest init` in `apps/admin/` to generate `components.json`\n2. Configure paths to match the existing `src/components/ui/` directory\n3. Set CSS variables mode (to allow token bridging later)\n4. Install required Radix primitive packages and `class-variance-authority` (already present), `clsx`, `tailwind-merge`\n5. Migrate existing 4 components (badge, card, table, tabs) to proper shadcn format if needed\n6. Ensure Tailwind CSS 4 config is compatible with shadcn CSS variable output\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- `apps/admin/components.json` exists with correct configuration\n- Existing 4 components are properly registered\n- `npx shadcn add button` works correctly\n- TypeScript types compile without errors",
  "status": "in_progress",
  "priority": 2,
